18:31.527 --> 18:34.201
Get out of my brother's body,
you evil triangle!

18:34.363 --> 18:36.161
Whoa!
Children fighting.

18:36.365 --> 18:37.617
I can sell this.

18:38.701 --> 18:40.920
Aah!
You can't stop me.

18:41.120 --> 18:43.919
I am a being of pure energy
with no weakness.

18:44.081 --> 18:44.957
(grunts)

18:45.124 --> 18:47.752
True, but you're
in Dipper's body.

18:47.918 --> 18:50.091
And I know
all his weaknesses.

18:50.296 --> 18:51.297
What do you mean
"his--?"

18:51.505 --> 18:52.301
Tickle, tickle.

18:52.506 --> 18:54.258
( Iaughil19 )

18:54.467 --> 18:56.390
Aah!
Body spasms.

18:56.594 --> 18:57.595
What are these?

18:57.762 --> 18:59.184
A little note
about the human body.

18:59.388 --> 19:01.811
You haven't slept
in over 24 hours.

19:02.016 --> 19:03.268
Also,
I got a full night's sleep

19:03.476 --> 19:05.478
and I'm on four
mega shots of Mabel juice.

19:05.645 --> 19:06.521
( Panting )

19:06.729 --> 19:08.276
What is this feeling?

19:08.439 --> 19:10.612
My body is burning.

19:10.816 --> 19:13.035
I can't move
these stupid noodle legs.

19:13.235 --> 19:15.363
Curse you,
useless flesh sticks.

19:15.571 --> 19:17.790
Body shutting down,

19:17.990 --> 19:19.742
must scratch,

19:19.950 --> 19:21.372
mosquito bites.

19:26.916 --> 19:28.918
Whoa! Whoa! Whoa!
Whoa! Hey!

19:32.004 --> 19:32.926
What?

19:33.130 --> 19:33.926
Yes!

19:34.131 --> 19:35.474
I'm in my own body

19:35.675 --> 19:39.054
and it's just as
underwhelming as I remember.

19:39.261 --> 19:40.137
(groans)

19:40.346 --> 19:41.188
Everything hurts.

19:41.389 --> 19:42.766
( Evil laughter )

19:45.101 --> 19:47.775
This isn't the last
you'll hear of me.

19:47.978 --> 19:49.195
Big things are coming.

19:49.397 --> 19:50.740
You can't stop me.

19:50.940 --> 19:52.362
I'm sorry, Gabe.

20:02.201 --> 20:04.295
( Opera music playing )

20:22.096 --> 20:23.439
Don't worry.

20:23.639 --> 20:25.812
I've seen enough movies
to know this is the part

20:26.016 --> 20:26.767
where the audience thinks

20:26.976 --> 20:29.525
it was all part of the show
and loves it.

20:29.729 --> 20:31.356
Cue applause!

20:31.522 --> 20:33.570
( Crowd booing )

20:39.697 --> 20:40.539
Gabe!

20:40.740 --> 20:42.458
Stick around
for the wrap party?

20:42.658 --> 20:44.456
We got mini quiches.

20:44.660 --> 20:46.378
Don't speak to me, Mabel.

20:46.579 --> 20:48.752
You've made a mockery
of my art form.

20:48.956 --> 20:50.048
Let's go, my loves.

20:50.249 --> 20:52.627
( Kissing )

20:52.835 --> 20:54.929
Did he just make out
with his puppets?

20:55.129 --> 20:57.552
I might have dodged
a bullet there.

20:57.757 --> 20:58.758
( Speaking in
foreign language )

21:00.509 --> 21:01.431
Oof!

21:01.635 --> 21:03.433
Mabel,
I'm sorry about all this.

21:03.637 --> 21:05.355
It's my fault
your puppets got ruined.

21:05.556 --> 21:07.058
Well,
one of them survived.

21:07.266 --> 21:09.018
And she has something
to say to you.

21:09.226 --> 21:11.149
I'm sorry, Dipper.

21:11.353 --> 21:14.607
I spent all week
obsessing over a dumb guy.

21:14.815 --> 21:18.285
But the dumb guy I should
have cared about was you.

21:18.444 --> 21:19.286
Bah!

21:19.445 --> 21:21.072
Mystery twins.

21:21.280 --> 21:22.623
Mystery twins.

21:22.823 --> 21:24.040
Ow!

21:24.200 --> 21:25.873
What did
Bill do to my hand?

21:26.076 --> 21:26.918
Aah!

21:27.119 --> 21:28.712
Nothing
a little sleep can't fix.

21:28.913 --> 21:31.837
Come on, bro bro,
let's go home.

21:31.999 --> 21:33.626
Seriously, I need to
go to the hospital.

21:33.834 --> 21:35.211
Hey, Dipper.

21:35.419 --> 21:38.719
What did one sock puppet say
to the other sock puppet?

21:38.881 --> 21:39.757
I don't know, Mabel.

21:39.924 --> 21:40.800
What?

21:41.008 --> 21:43.636
You look like
you could use a hand.

21:43.803 --> 21:44.929
( Iaughil19 )

21:47.306 --> 21:49.684
That joke
was really something.

21:49.892 --> 21:51.940
Yeah, something terrible.

21:52.144 --> 21:53.521
( Iaughil19 )

21:54.855 --> 21:55.947
( screaming )
